
  Welcome,

  This package will update PureBasic 1.40 to 1.43. You need to have the
  PureBasic 1.40 full version correctly installed on your hard drive.


  Installation:
  -------------

  Use the supplied install script, select your langage and select the
  drawer where PureBasic is installed (theorically 'PureBasic:')

  Once the install script has finish its job, just launch PureBasic
  and check the title bar to see if the update has been performed
  ('PureBasic 1.43' should be visible).


  Informations about this update:
  -------------------------------

  Fixed: LoadPicture()
  Fixed: File library (ReadXXXX functions was corrupted)
  Fixed: AddSprite()
  Fixed: Chunky library (C2P was bugged)
  Fixed: UseGadgetList()
  Fixed: Some compiler bugs...

  Updated: Timer & Sound deutsch guides
  Updated: Index guide.


  Future:
  -------

  The next major update should be the 1.50 and will include 3 new libraries:

    - Protracker replay library
    - Popup menu library
    - New Timer library


      Thank you,

          The Fantaisie Software Team



